===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A mechanical device intended to make a task easier.
# Equipment used in a profession, e.g., ''tools of the trade''.
# {{slang}} A complete idiot.
# {{slang}} Penis.
# {{slang}} A person who uncritically supports and assists established authority. See [[sell out]].
# {{slang}} By association, any contemptible, inadequate, or unpleasant person.
# {{slang}} A person who is used in relationships for reasons other than love.



===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|tool||}}

# To work on or shape with tools, e.g., ''hand-tooled leather''.
# To equip with tools.
# To work very hard.

